{"tid":302990,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 如何Mr依家同大家交代清楚或者道歉 大家會唔會都機會佢地","createTime":"2017-06-29T21:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T06:35:26.000Z","uid":16086,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f30688ac8b192ff65d651da205b8240a5376383","tid":302990,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T21:51:47.000Z","msg":"首先，我係前設左 Mr. 以前嘅作品係有抄襲嘅<br />\n網上亦都有好多討論同論證，所以我就唔多講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fn06e6PgL5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFn06e6PgL5g&d=eYN5qp62t%2FYRX7NkV8K1nC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3904d18e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fn06e6PgL5g</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. 因為被指抄歌喺網上已經淪為過街老鼠，<br />\n而佢地嘅音樂生涯都收曬皮咁滯<br />\n不過估唔到兩個月之前竟然會出咗首新歌<br />\n個人覺得幾好 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(不過唔講太多，唔想比人當打手)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁有新歌出，姐係有機會未來會繼續出<br />\n不過當年嘅醜聞咁大單，再紅翻嘅話<br />\n反對聲音一定會再次出現<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n真心，其實我覺得 Mr. 最柒嘅唔係抄歌，<br />\n而係抄完唔認<br />\n嗰時佢地都真係出緊名，面對咁大嘅負面批評，<br />\n唔識點面對我覺得都情有可原<br />\n到依家2017啦，佢地竟然仲出歌<br />\n我覺得佢地對音樂係有熱誠嘅<br />\n作為支持本地音樂嘅人，真心想見到有熱誠嘅唱歌人<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地痛改前非，承認錯誤，大家會唔會比機會佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(真心唔想曬左隊band)</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb9e2ee6ba5049bc48d958849bde0e74890ea1e6","tid":302990,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:51:08.000Z","msg":"比 正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔比 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f659219bf7092267c9ef2269b5a8aa671bb57e48","tid":302990,"uid":71411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:53:13.000Z","msg":"香港本土多數過街老鼠"},{"pid":"e4fdf6230be17ec60628e550c234ffc3cdb56d21","tid":302990,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s